txt.en: 'The goblins of Draugdegil have grown too bold. We must make an offensive move against them soon, lest they grow even more powerful.\n\n'Enter into Draugdegil, north from Helethir and inside the gate at Fennas Guldur, and seek out the goblins there. The goblins of Dol Guldur have been training the fell Wargs to carry them into battle...we must put an end to them before it is too late!'
'This is only the begining of a very long task, but thank you for your aid, [placeholder].'
If left unchecked, the goblins of Draugdegil will soon overrun Helethir.
Goblins can be found at Draugdegil, north of Helethir and just inside the gate and Fennas Guldur.
Haukur is at Helethir, south from the gate at Fennas Guldur.\n\nYou should return to Haukur for your reward.
